      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a superlative E46 M3 in collector-grade condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies to an 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach: the VANOS unit has been overhauled, rod bearings replaced, and the rear subframe reinforced\u2014comprehensively addressing all platform-specific weak points. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox shifts with bolt-action precision, and the factory limited-slip differential provides optimal torque distribution. The chassis remains taut, riding on refreshed bushings and OEM dampers that preserve the original suspension geometry. Finished in Alpine White over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the exterior retains a deep luster with zero evidence of oxidation or road rash. This is a turn-key, preservation-class specimen for the most discerning automotive purist.",
